CharMotivation.Name: Ambition
CharMotivation.Notes: Her dealings with the Pyke crime syndicate has given Sin the taste of the good life, and she plans lie, cheat, and steal her way to the top.

CharObligation.Name: Criminal
CharObligation.Notes: Sin has connections with the Pyke crime syndicate due to her shady property dealings. And they tend to call in favors.

Character.Story:
Sin comes from a long line of bounty hunters and learned many of their ways, even though she did not join in the family business. The Rodian came to Coruscant ten years ago seeking ever larger fortunes and wrestled her way into the property market. What Sin thought was an innocuous deal turned out to involve the Pykes, and they made sure she would profit more if she undercut her original client deeply. In time, Sin came to appreciate the world of crime and what could be accomplished working outside of the system.
• You have had limited experience with Zelcomm Industries, having sold some office space in the same tower. There seems to be as much freight going into and out of the office building as through a small starport. Rumors say that Zelcomm is a front for weapons muggling. • Though innately talented with blasters, you have found that a concealed vibroknife can work in places a blaster can’t, and you have taught yourself how to use one effectively. • Finally, when your silver tongue doesn’t do the trick, a couple of credits can smooth over a tense negotiation.
